name: SLOLife
0:
”Alexa, start slow Life”
”Alexa, ask slow Life for something fun to do”
”Alexa, tell slow Life I am bored”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: slow life
des: This is a simple skill to help you find fun things to do in San Luis Obispo County. San Luis Obispo County is full of opportunities to get outdoors and experience central coast living. Even long term residents most likely will find activities in the SLO Life skill that they have never experienced. There are activities for people of all ages and skills in SLO Life.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
